        <section id="detailed_desc">
            <p>The callback for the second instance.</p>
            <p>The SDK triggers this callback when it cannot connect to the server 10 seconds after calling the <apiname keyref="videoSourceJoinChannel"/> method, regardless of whether it is in the channel. If the SDK fails to rejoin the channel 20 minutes after being disconnected from Agora&apos;s edge server, the SDK stops rejoining the channel.</p>
        </section>
